HEADWORD: Indeliberate
<hw>In`de*lib"er*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>indeliberatus</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not, and
<er>Deliberate</er>.]</ety> <def>Done without deliberation;
unpremeditated.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> --
<wordforms><wf>In`de*lib"er*ate*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms>⟦br⟧
